  "valid_count": 13,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q0",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q0\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia con exponente racional a índice de raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considera la siguiente expresión:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mn>16</mn>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al escribir esta expresión en forma de raíz, ¿qué número corresponde al índice de la raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q1",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q1\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un laboratorio químico se estudia el volumen\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mi>V</mi>\n      </math>\n      (en litros) de una solución. Para cierto cálculo se utiliza\n      la potencia\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>.\n      ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa la misma\n      cantidad usando el símbolo de raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <mi>V</mi>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <mroot>\n              <mi>V</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msqrt>\n            <mi>V</mi>\n          </msqrt>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>V</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q2",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q2\"\n    title=\"Interpretación de exponente fraccionario en contexto de dinero\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un banco se modela el crecimiento de un ahorro usando el factor\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mn>1,05</mn>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cómo se puede interpretar con palabras esta potencia?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        Dividir <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1,05</mn></math> por\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Calcular la raíz cuadrada de\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1,05</mn></math>, es decir,\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mn>1,05</mn>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        Calcular la raíz cuadrada de\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1,05</mn></math> y luego elevar ese resultado a\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        Calcular la raíz cúbica de\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1,05</mn></math>, es decir,\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mn>1,05</mn>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q3",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q3\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Un estudiante está repasando potencias con exponente fraccionario y debe reescribir la expresión\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mn>7</mn>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>\n      usando raíz enésima, en una forma del tipo\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mroot>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n            <mi>m</mi>\n          </msup>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mroot>\n      </math>.\n      ¿Cuál de las siguientes alternativas corresponde a esa expresión?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msqrt>\n            <msup>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </msqrt>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <mroot>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q4",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q4\"\n    title=\"Conversión de raíz enésima a exponente racional en contexto geométrico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En el desarrollo de un ejercicio de geometría sobre volúmenes, aparece la siguiente expresión:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mroot>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mn>5</mn>\n        </mroot>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>El profesor pide escribirla como una potencia de base \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mi>a</mi>\n      </math>\n      con exponente racional, es decir, de la forma\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mi>□</mi>\n            <mi>□</mi>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>.\n      ¿Cuál de las siguientes fracciones completa correctamente el exponente?\n    </p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q5",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q5\"\n    title=\"Interpretación de raíz como exponente racional en un modelo de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Para describir cómo aumenta la precisión de un reloj astronómico a medida que pasa el tiempo, una científica propone el siguiente modelo para el error acumulado, medido en microsegundos:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>E</mi>\n          <mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mroot>\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>t</mi>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>En este modelo, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> representa el tiempo transcurrido, en segundos, desde que el reloj se sincroniza con una señal de referencia, hasta un máximo de 10 000 segundos.</p>\n    <p>La científica quiere explicar esta expresión usando potencias con exponente racional, en lugar de raíces. ¿Cuál de las siguientes descripciones corresponde correctamente a la expresión anterior?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        El error es proporcional a <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> elevado a un medio.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        El error es proporcional a <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> elevado a dos tercios.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        El error es proporcional a <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> elevado a tres medios.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        El error es proporcional a <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> elevado a tres cuartos.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q6",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q6\"\n    title=\"Conversión de exponente racional a raíz en contexto estadístico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un estudio estadístico sobre los tiempos de atención en un servicio, se utiliza el siguiente modelo para el tiempo promedio, en minutos, en función del número de personas en la fila <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow></math>:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>·</mo><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup></mrow></math>\n    </p>\n    <p>El analista desea reescribir el factor <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup></mrow></math> como una raíz de índice 4, dejando el exponente 3 dentro del signo radical. ¿Cuál de las siguientes igualdades es correcta?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mroot><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mn>4</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mroot><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mroot><mi>t</mi><mn>4</mn></mroot><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow></math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q7",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q7\"\n    title=\"Conversión de exponente racional a raíz en contexto de medición\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento químico, la concentración de cierta sustancia después de un proceso se modela con la expresión\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>0,8</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      gramos por litro.</p>\n    <p>Para registrar el resultado en un informe, se desea expresar\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>0,8</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      usando notación de raíz. ¿Cuál de las siguientes opciones corresponde a esa expresión?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>0,8</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>0,8</mn>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mroot>\n                <mn>0,8</mn>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mroot>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>0,8</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q8",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q8\"\n    title=\"Conversión de raíz a exponente racional en contexto de ahorro\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un modelo para estimar el interés compuesto de un ahorro, se usa la siguiente expresión para representar el crecimiento de un monto inicial:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>M</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>En esta expresión, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>M</mi></mrow></math> representa el monto inicial invertido, en pesos. Para escribir esta expresión en una planilla de cálculo que solo admite potencias con exponente racional del tipo <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mfrac></msup></mrow></math>, ¿cuál de las siguientes opciones la representa correctamente?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>M</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>M</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>M</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>M</mi>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q9",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q9\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un informe de laboratorio se utiliza la siguiente tabla para comparar dos formas de escribir una misma expresión: con potencia de exponente fraccionario y con raíz.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes opciones completa correctamente la segunda fila?</p>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Notación exponencial</th>\n          <th>Notación radical equivalente</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mn>1</mn>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mroot>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </mroot>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mo>(</mo>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                    <mo>)</mo>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <mn>5</mn>\n                  </mfrac>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n          <td>...</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mo>(</mo>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                    <mo>)</mo>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mo>(</mo>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                    <mo>)</mo>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mo>(</mo>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                    <mo>)</mo>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q10",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q10\"\n    title=\"Conversión de radical a exponente racional en contexto científico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un laboratorio de física, la intensidad <em>I</em> (en unidades arbitrarias) que llega a un detector se relaciona con la potencia <em>P</em> (en watts) mediante la siguiente expresión radical:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>I</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>P</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>En los experimentos se trabaja con potencias del orden de 80 000 W, por lo que resulta más conveniente escribir esta relación usando una potencia con exponente racional en lugar del símbolo de raíz.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes ecuaciones representa correctamente la misma relación entre <em>I</em> y <em>P</em> usando un exponente racional?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>I</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>P</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>I</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>P</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>I</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>P</mi>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>I</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mi>P</mi>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q11",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q11\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz en contexto de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un informe sobre el uso de una sala de estudio, una investigadora modela la cantidad de estudiantes presentes en función del tiempo <em>t</em> (medido en horas) mediante la expresión\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup></mrow></math>.\n      Para presentarla de otra forma, quiere escribir esta potencia como una raíz enésima equivalente.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones corresponde a esa misma cantidad escrita con notación de raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><msup><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup><mn>4</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><msup><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></msup><mn>5</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><mrow><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></msup><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><mn>4</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q12",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q12\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz en un producto triple\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considera la siguiente expresión exponencial, en la que todo el producto está elevado al mismo exponente racional:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>2</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>7</mn>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente, escrita usando notación de raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>7</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>7</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mo>·</mo>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mo>·</mo>\n                <mn>7</mn>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>7</mn>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 12
    }
  ]
